 Board Of Education To Promulgate Regulations To Implement Such Administrative Consolidation; To Provide A Two-year Waiver From Accountability And State Assessment Requirements For The New Student Population; To Amend Section 37-7-103, Mississippi Code Of 1972, In Conformity; And For Related Purposes.</description><committee/><history><step><date>2013-01-21</date><action>Referred To Education</action><chamber>S</chamber><chamber_id>58</chamber_id><importance>1</importance></step><step><date>2013-01-29</date><action>Title Suff Do Pass Comm Sub</action><chamber>S</chamber><chamber_id>58</chamber_id><importance>0</importance></step><step><date>2013-02-13</date><action>Committee Substitute Adopted</action><chamber>S</chamber><chamber_id>58</chamber_id><importance>0</importance></step><step><date>2013-02-13</date><action>Amended</action><chamber>S</chamber><chamber_id>58</chamber_id><importance>0</importance></step><step><date>2013-02-13</date><action>Passed As Amended</action><chamber>S</chamber><chamber_id>58</chamber_id><importance>1</importance></step><step><date>2013-02-14</date><action>Motion to Reconsider Entered</action><chamber>S</chamber><chamber_id>58</chamber_id><importance>0</importance></step><step><date>2013-02-15</date><action>Reconsidered</action><chamber>S</chamber><chamber_id>58</chamber_id><importance>0</importance></step><step><date>2013-02-15</date><action>Amended</action><chamber>S</chamber><chamber_id>58</chamber_id><importance>0</importance></step><step><date>2013-02-15</date><action>Passed As Amended</action><chamber>S</chamber><chamber_id>58</chamber_id><importance>0</importance></step><step><date>2013-02-19</date><action>Transmitted To House</action><chamber>S</chamber><chamber_id>58</chamber_id><importance>0</importance></step><step><date>2013-02-21</date><action>Referred To Education</action><chamber>H</chamber><chamber_id>57</chamber_id><importance>1</importance></step><step><date>2013-03-05</date><action>Title Suff Do Pass As Amended</acti